        Tools to test every aspect of your screen — from dead pixels to touch accuracy & refresh rate. Works on all devices.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#tests" class="btn-primary">Start Testing</a>
        <a href="/report" class="btn-secondary">View Display Report</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Live Device Stats -->
